# Public Mapbox token — used to render the real Bondi map on the home page.
# Sign up at https://mapbox.com → Account → Tokens → copy the "Default public token".
# 50,000 free static-image requests per month, no card required.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your token:
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1...
